title: ICoordinateSystemFeatureData.IGetYAxisEntities
description: Gets the entities for the y axis of this coordinate system feature.

parameters.name: Count
parameters.description: Number of entities for the y axis

returns: in-process, unmanaged C++: Pointer to an an array of entities for the y axis VBA, VB.NET, C#, and C++/CLI: Not supported See In-process Methods for details about this type of method.
remarks:
Call
ICoordinateSystemFeatureData::GetYAxisEntitiesCount
before calling this method to get Count.
See SOLIDWORKS Help for a list of valid entities.
